t/uploads/2025/01/FoB-Combs-Matthews-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/FoB-Combs-Matthews-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/FoB-Combs-Matthews-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/FoB-Combs-Matthews-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/FoB-Combs-Matthews-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>波士顿召唤音乐节 (Boston Calling Festival) 将于五月回归， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fall-out-boy">Fall Out Boy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/luke-combs">Luke Combs</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-matthews-band">Dave Matthews Band</a>将成为阵亡将士纪念日周末活动的主角。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fall-out-boy-interview-pete-wentz-download-2024-so-much-for-stardust-future-3533990">《打倒男孩》告诉我们有关 2024 年下载的头条新闻：“我们希望人们在他们的怪异方面表现出色”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该音乐节将于 5 月 23 日至 25 日在波士顿下奥尔斯顿 (Lower Allston) 附近的哈佛体育中心 (Harvard Athletic Complex) 回归，乡村明星库姆斯 (Combs) 将为周五闭幕。同样在同一天， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-moroney">Megan Moroney</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sheryl-crow">Sheryl Crow</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/t-pain">T-Pain</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tlc">TLC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/infinity-song">Infinity Song</a> 、Kyle Dion、Bebe Stockwell 和 Holy Roller 等明星也将亮相。</p><p>流行朋克巨擘 Fall Out Boy 将成为周六的主角，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">艾薇儿</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cage-the-elephant">Cage The Elephant</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-black-crowes">The Black Crowes</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/all-time-low">All Time Low</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-bay">James Bay</a> 、The Maine、Lucius 和 Valley 等乐队也将加入其中。</p><p> 2024 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-roll-hall-of-fame-2024-ozzy-osbourne-cher-and-more-to-be-inducted-3749163">摇滚名人堂入选者戴夫·马修斯乐队 (Dave Matthews Band)</a>将于周日结束音乐节，随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vampire-weekend">Vampire Weekend</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sublime">Sublime</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/public-enemy">Public Enemy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/remi-wolf">Remi Wolf</a> 、Goth Babe、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">Tom Morello</a> 、The 502s 和 Spin Doctors 等艺术家将进行表演。</p><p>一系列当地和崭露头角的艺术家也将在周末演奏 Boston Calling，包括 Timmy Skelly、Simon Robert French、Rebuilder、Sidebody、Pinklids、Mo Lowda &amp; The Humble、Mon Rovîa 和 Amble。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEfeQlmt6zu/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 